{"tid":501494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞 不滿美國承認耶路撒冷是首都,揚言派兵耶路撒冷","createTime":"2017-12-17T02:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T13:27:40.000Z","uid":53705,"like":117,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"87ce1d34abca1fccaeeb08482c02ce4e5692789c","tid":501494,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171211/1070574.htm?t=%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%81%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E3%80%8C%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B5%E8%80%B6%E8%B7%AF%E6%92%92%E5%86%B7%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82OK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171211%2F1070574.htm%3Ft%3D%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25EF%25BC%2581%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2585%25B5%25E8%2580%25B6%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2592%2592%25E5%2586%25B7%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582OK&d=l5NSWSY8HZggNMti%2Ba%2FOoMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=43bdf69f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171211/1070574.htm?t=%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%EF%BC%81%E9%A6%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9E%E5%B7%B2%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E3%80%8C%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B5%E8%80%B6%E8%B7%AF%E6%92%92%E5%86%B7%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%EF%BC%9A%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82OK</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普7日承認耶路撒冷為以色列首都，引起全球穆斯林激憤，也使國際社會擔憂。包括聯合國、歐盟、英國、法國、巴勒斯坦、伊朗、土耳其也紛紛指責美國破壞地區和平。馬來西亞國防部長希山慕丁（Hishammuddin Hussein）甚至表示，馬國的軍隊也準備好向耶路撒冷進軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞vs以色列<br />\n世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a6360bd48ca95b0f1ba1dd0ed9ec691e22227f","tid":501494,"uid":51701,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:18:49.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞算世俗都..."},{"pid":"7641bf7cd17665b494a05a788d422455078c595d","tid":501494,"uid":51701,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞不承認以色列，和以色列也沒有外交關係，故此馬來西亞護照上用馬來文和英文印上「本護照於各國有效，以色列除外。」的字句。但是以色列政府仍會向到訪的馬來西亞公民在另一張紙上發給入境簽證，但如果回國後被移民局發現的話護照將會被隨即沒收，且也會禁止出國一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n實際上，馬來西亞政府允許信仰基督教的馬來西亞公民以宗教理由前往以色列。2009年，以巴衝突升級，政府以安全理由禁止公民前往以色列，直到2011年才撤銷禁令。但是卻對基督徒採取更嚴厲的朝聖措施，這包括每年只允許700人前往以色列，每個教堂的朝聖團限制在40人以下，3年內只能朝聖一次，每次只可以在以色列旅遊最多10天，不能以私人名義前往以色列，以及朝聖者必須超過18歲等等。<br />\n<br />\n2012年12月19日，馬來西亞政府正式放寬基督徒前往以色朝聖的限制，不再限制朝聖者的年齡、每年的朝聖人數、朝聖次數和教會朝聖團人數，同時允許基督徒在當地逗留長達21天。[3]"},{"pid":"7a01566482f946503356cbbc13d2d5309409a363","tid":501494,"uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"星加坡夾係馬拉同印尼中間, 都咪話唔驚"},{"pid":"238cf3a4d19dd10d8f66927d38c678153781ccdd","tid":501494,"uid":139766,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:23:43.000Z","msg":"派兵開戰吧 <br />\n反正第三次世界大戰都將會係宗教戰<br />\n穆士林 V.s 異教徒  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eee330aefa86f81a6fb489037511f43bc2ff007","tid":501494,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"引發世界大戰WW3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953fc839fccf9c6d8ebff944a9a1054a5dba85d7","tid":501494,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>派兵開戰吧 <br />\n反正第三次世界大戰都將會係宗教戰<br />\n穆士林 V.s 異教徒  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji