ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發癲都冇用<br />\n三個故仔同源</blockquote><br />\n精神無問題、智力正常都唔會做耶撚啦"},{"pid":"482cba36f7ebcaddb833481d0bdd2128e4d58f2c","tid":501494,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解回教同耶教嘅聖地都係耶路撒冷？</blockquote><br />\n三敎同源<br />\n三個宗教其實都係信同一個上帝</blockquote><br />\n有d耶撚聽到呢句會發癲</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前同個耶撚講，即刻發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係多口同耶撚上司講於是無咗份工</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神不可以被證明不存在 呢個是神存在的邏輯立足點 縱使有奧克削銻刀  咁你信耶穌存在都覺無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但好多呢d耶撚 唔讀歴史，唔知教義<br />\n<br />\n回教認耶穌係先知(不過outdated 最新果個是穆罕默德 所以佢傳達神的旨意先係最近)<br />\n<br />\n猶太教將耶穌都做神棍一條"},{"pid":"42ebb9b36c47c73cbb732cf0d3e6aeee722185d9","tid":501494,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n三敎同源<br />\n三個宗教其實都係信同一個上帝</blockquote><br />\n有d耶撚聽到呢句會發癲</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前同個耶撚講，即刻發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係多口同耶撚上司講於是無咗份工</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神不可以被證明不存在 呢個是神存在的邏輯立足點 縱使有奧克削銻刀  咁你信耶穌存在都覺無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但好多呢d耶撚 唔讀歴史，唔知教義<br />\n<br />\n回教認耶穌係先知(不過outdated 最新果個是穆罕默德 所以佢傳達神的旨意先係最準確)<br />\n<br />\n猶太教將耶穌都做神棍一條</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9715e6060381575d8da3705dbd6e52acac635b35","tid":501494,"uid":29804,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>基本上三個教都係抄 瑣羅亞斯德教(拜火教、祆教)<br />\n<br />\n猶太教 自 瑣羅亞斯德教而嚟<br />\n基督宗教 自 猶太教二次創作<br />\n回教 自 基督宗教 三次創作<br />\n<br />\n次次都係有條友話自己係神使者 或 先知 或 仔<br />\n<br />\n又有人信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基督宗教已經包埋天主教？</blockquote><br />\n應該係</blockquote><br />\n猶太教 抄左部份 瑣羅亞斯德教 教義<br />\n基督宗教 係猶太教故仔續集，個續集內容又抄返瑣羅亞斯德教<br />\n回教 阿穆罕默德抄耶穌傳教方式，周街變魔術，個故仔就抄返猶太教(即係舊約)，七八成一樣<br />\n<br />\n啲故仔重用再重用都有人信，到而家仲挷埋炸彈去自殺<br />\n所以人其實好撚蠢"},{"pid":"13892ab846eaa07b5627ea0114dc1f2525279986","tid":501494,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n三敎同源<br />\n三個宗教其實都係信同一個上帝</blockquote><br />\n有d耶撚聽到呢句會發癲</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前同個耶撚講，即刻發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係多口同耶撚上司講於是無咗份工</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神不可以被證明不存在 呢個是神存在的邏輯立足點 縱使有奧克削銻刀  咁你信耶穌存在都覺無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但好多呢d耶撚 唔讀歴史，唔知教義<br />\n<br />\n回教認耶穌係先知(不過outdated 最新果個是穆罕默德 所以佢傳達神的旨意先係最近)<br />\n<br />\n猶太教將耶穌都做神棍一條</blockquote><br />\n回教認為耶穌的教導和留下的經書已被篡改<br />\n耶和華神於是親自寫古蘭經再搵天使讀俾穆罕默德聽"},{"pid":"ef58dbb2da5a98ca7159b76b2d65d3b538ae770f","tid":501494,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":