gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f548b21ad69c766fd9eaf99e9aac576490198171","tid":501494,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://crazypic.ck101.com/7/e/7e7d134438a0a6436e36360911e9e28c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrazypic.ck101.com%2F7%2Fe%2F7e7d134438a0a6436e36360911e9e28c.png&h=081a8950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球軍事力量排名<br />\n馬來西亞原來排第28名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60293ba3fe2f101a2b6addd703e3fe08ebddadab","tid":501494,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://crazypic.ck101.com/7/e/7e7d134438a0a6436e36360911e9e28c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrazypic.ck101.com%2F7%2Fe%2F7e7d134438a0a6436e36360911e9e28c.png&h=081a8950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球軍事力量排名<br />\n馬來西亞原來排第28名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印尼都高過以色列？<br />\n<br />\n埃及仲要高咁多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5556ca0556061b7637d4ff885b2fd76d75f1d44d","tid":501494,"uid":136303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>世俗化都咁多咀炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十足怨婦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真果句<br />\n耶路撒冷 係伊斯蘭既聖地, 家陣比以色列佔領<br />\n你都嬲啦<br />\n<br />\n舉個例子, 有幾個大陸人佔領你間房, 趕你出客廳, 你嬲唔嬲??</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過麥加呀？唔係個個光頭佬喎"},{"pid":"c27a1c46c97dd041cedbb4288bff890eb88dac0a","tid":501494,"uid":31076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"其實出兵係有可能做到<br />\n<br />\n30年前英國都已經可以去到好遠打阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n而家既馬拉做唔到就真係廢得緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過去到，打唔打得贏就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543c5f78edeb86fc227a97e1c629c744312ab48a","tid":501494,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"1936年Great Arab Revolt 阿拉伯起義推翻英國殖民統治，英國設立Palestine Royal Commission,研究阿拉伯起義既原因，發現&quot;兩個人種想統治同一領土&quot;<br />\n，提出兩國方案，領土分佈如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/145836_ebc6a2bba25b379545d48d4c4781ac3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F145836_ebc6a2bba25b379545d48d4c4781ac3c.jpg&h=99640000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次兩國方案，猶太人領土遠比阿拉伯人少<br />\n猶太人態度：接受          阿拉伯人態度：拒絕<br />\n<br />\n第二次兩國方案，由聯合國提出<br />\n領土分佈如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/150325_f38cbe197f50a94c3d024f59b8e86180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F150325_f38cbe197f50a94c3d024f59b8e86180.jpg&h=3abbf6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n猶太人態度：第二次接受          阿拉伯人態度：第二次拒絕"},{"pid":"ed9616a412e2ad5d290d4f984d4b2a0487181098","tid":501494,"uid":148989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實出兵係有可能做到<br />\n<br />\n30年前英國都已經可以去到好遠打阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n而家既馬拉做唔到就真係廢得緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過去到，打唔打得贏就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n皇家海軍當年成支艦隊攻過去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年皇家海軍2部航母加一堆登陸艦先搶番Falklands 返黎&hellip;&hellip;仲要有唔小損傷<br />\n<br />\n馬拉支海軍成堆細船，無航母無登陸艦，打條毛咩"},{"pid":"231015e98a7db2ec1275d48841e3ab759266c7f8","tid":501494,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"緊接第二次兩國方案，1947-1948年，巴勒斯坦社區爆發暴亂，1948-1949年，埃及，伊拉克，敘利亞等多國加入，爆發全面戰爭<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯人態度：第三次拒絕"},{"pid":"1514ffef7329989fb21bf3fc0475bc857cb4e5bd","tid":501494,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"1949年，以色列勝利，取得東耶路撒冷，西岸以外既國境全土<br />\n<br />\n1967年戰爭，亦即係著名既六日戰爭，阿拉伯人聯盟再次從東南北方嘗試攻擊以色列，但以色列取得壓倒勝利，取得東耶路薩冷，西岸，加沙地帶<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯人態度：第四次拒絕<br />\n<br />\n1967年，阿拉伯人聯盟聚集埃及，發表Three Nos<br />\nNo Peace, No Recognition, No Negotiation<br />\n<br />\n第四次拒絕之中，阿拉伯人展現其暴戾本性"},{"pid":"066e11234ac7d7aa5e05a146e5ca71836efb7ac5","tid":501494,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"2000年，喺美國時任總統克林頓安排下，以色列總理得以同永遠say no 既一方 - 巴勒斯坦自治區主席見面，史稱2000 Camp David Summit <br />\n<br />\n以色列歸還加沙地帶，西岸大部份地帶，能以東耶路薩冷為首都<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯人態度：第五次拒絕<br />\n&quot;He did not negotiate in good faith; indeed, he did not negotiate at all. He just kept saying no to every offer, never making any counterproposals of his own,&quot;"},{"pid":"bd427afe04d2a3e9784ad6bc78a78a7d4b6a019d","tid":501494,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:10:53.000Z","msg":"2005 年，以色列無條件放棄加沙地帶，並從加沙撤軍，撤走猶太人社區，歸還主治兩權於巴勒斯坦人<br />\n<br />\n但係，亦成為近年臭名昭著既 哈瑪斯 激進組織既溫床<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯人：第六次拒絕"},{"pid":"fe0ca15cdebee36792c740e4472ab0fe112564f1","tid":501494,"uid":50018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲Muslim國家全部都咁小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地視宗教自由，人權為無物，通姦者受石形而死（stoned to death),異教徒要斬頭（behead)<br />\n當佢地趕絕infidels 成為100%伊斯蘭教徒時，並冇帶比佢地心目中既理想國度，佢地只係不斷包裝自己為受害